   <conbody>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <fig class="- topic/fig ">
               <image href="../Images/Profibus_Parts_LEDs_0000411656.svg"
                      scope="local"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </fig>
            <table class="- topic/table ">
               <tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                  <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="15.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="20.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="COLSPEC2" colwidth="20.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="COLSPEC0" colwidth="6.00*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Part</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Name</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Status when
working correctly</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Description</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(1)</b>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Online</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">On (green)</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Off: Profibus-DP
bus gateway is offline.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Constant green:
Profibus-DP bus gateway is online.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(2)</b>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Offline</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Off</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Off: Profibus-DP
bus gateway is online.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Constant red:
Profibus-DP bus gateway is offline.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(3)</b>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Not used</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">—</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">—</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry morerows="3" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(4)</b>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="3" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Fieldbus diag</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="3" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Off</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Off: Gateway
initialization successful.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Flashing red
slowly (1 Hz): Gateway configuration error. The input and/or output
data length is invalid.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Flashing red
(2 Hz): Gateway configuration error. User parameter data length and/or
content is invalid.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Flashing red
fast (4 Hz): Error detected with the ASIC in charge of Profibus-DP
communications when resetting the gateway.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry morerows="3" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(5)</b>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="3" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Modbus</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="3" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">On (green)</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Off: No power.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Constant green:
Modbus communications OK.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Flashing green:
No Modbus communication.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Red: Loss of
communication with at least one secondary Modbus device. Exception
code coming from a command or a transaction.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry morerows="3" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(6)</b>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="3" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Gateway</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="3" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Flashing (green)</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Off: No power.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Constant green:
The gateway is currently being initialized and configured.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Flashing green:
The gateway is in running order, configuration OK.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Flashing red
and green: Configuration absent / not valid.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
         </sectiondiv>
         <p class="- topic/p ">When the LED <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(5)</b> is flashing red from
communication loss, the LED will revert to a green state when communication
is restored. When the LED <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(5)</b> is flashing red because of incorrect
values with the aperiodic read/write services, then the only way to
clear the error is to reuse these aperiodic services with correct
values.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">If the LED <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(6) </b> is flashing following a sequence
beginning with one or more red flashes, note down the order of this
sequence and save for troubleshooting. Powering off the gateway and
turning it back on again will solve the problem in some cases.</p>
      </section>
